  "profileInfo": {
    "title": "Important information",
    "lead": "Key rules to know about how the SAYIN GLOBAL platform works.",
    "statusTitle": "Status system (4 levels)",
    "statusBody": "Every user has an account status:\n• Good — no rule violations, no restrictions.\n• Warning — minor reports or problematic listings recorded.\n• Restricted — listing creation or messaging is temporarily limited.\n• Blocked — serious violations, account is blocked.\nYou can see your status on your profile page.",
    "ratingTitle": "Rating system",
    "ratingBody": "A rating consists of stars (1–5) and a written review. New accounts start at 0 stars — that's neutral, not untrusted. Only real buyers can leave a rating. A written review is required — ratings without comments are not accepted. Reviews can be translated between the 4 supported languages.",
    "moderationTitle": "Moderation process",
    "moderationBody": "Every new or edited listing goes into \"Pending review\". A moderator typically approves or rejects within a few hours. If rejected, the reason is shown in the user's interface language (translated to all 4 languages). Editing an active listing automatically sends it back to moderation.",
    "lifecycleTitle": "Listing lifecycle",
    "lifecycleBody": "• Active — visible and available for sale\n• Sold — marked sold by you, automatically deleted after 7 days\n• Rejected — rejected by moderation, automatically deleted after 5 days\n• Expired — past 30-day limit, automatically deleted\nYou can delete your own listing at any time.",
    "complaintTitle": "Complaints and consequences",
    "complaintBody": "Users can report listings or sellers. A moderator reviews each complaint:\n• Valid — the listing is removed and the seller's status is downgraded.\n• Invalid — no consequences.\nRepeated valid complaints lead to account blocking.",
    "rulesTitle": "Seller responsibilities and platform expectations",
    "rulesBody": "• Only sell animals you actually own.\n• Provide accurate, truthful information in listings.\n• Use high-quality, recent photos.\n• Communicate honestly and respectfully with buyers.\n• Mark sold listings as \"Sold\".\n• Spam, false information, or illegal items are prohibited."
  },
